                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <a id="hyp_processNote" title="Award Criteria" style="text-decoration: underline;color: #ffffff;text-transform: capitalize;cursor:pointer">
                                <span class="fa fa-info-circle fa-lg"></span>&nbsp;<b>Award Criteria</b>
